lead_paragraph: Two Russian swimmers filed an appeal Saturday against their exclusion from the Rio de Janeiro Olympics, claiming the ban is "invalid" and "unenforceable."

headline.print_headline: 2 Russian Swimmers File Appeals Against Olympic Ban
